    <h3>Core Web Vitals — Objetivos y Acciones</h3>
    <div class="table-wrap">
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Métrica</th><th>Objetivo</th><th>Cómo conseguirlo</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>LCP</strong> (Largest Contentful Paint)</td>
            <td>&lt; 2.5 seg</td>
            <td>Imagen hero en WebP preloaded, CDN para estáticos, hosting rápido</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>CLS</strong> (Cumulative Layout Shift)</td>
            <td>&lt; 0.1</td>
            <td>Dimensiones fijas en imágenes y embeds (Calendly, widget chatbot)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>INP</strong> (Interaction to Next Paint)</td>
            <td>&lt; 200ms</td>
            <td>Diferir scripts de terceros (GTM, Pixel, Clarity) con loading="lazy"</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>TTFB</strong> (Time to First Byte)</td>
            <td>&lt; 600ms</td>
            <td>Caché del servidor, evitar redirects innecesarios, hosting SSD</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
